Housing Land Supply Amendment Act 2023

An Act to amend the Housing Land Supply Act 2018
[Royal Assent 21 September 2023]

Be it enacted by Her Excellency the Governor of Tasmania, by and with the advice and consent of the Legislative Council and House of Assembly, in Parliament assembled, as follows:

1. Short title
    This Act may be cited as the Housing Land Supply Amendment Act 2023 .

2. Commencement
    This Act is taken to have commenced on the day on which the Housing Land Supply Act 2018 commenced.

3. Principal Act
    In this Act, the Housing Land Supply Act 2018 is referred to as the Principal Act.

4.
    The amendments effected by this section have been incorporated into the authorised version of the Housing Land Supply Act 2018 .

5.
    The amendments effected by this section have been incorporated into the authorised version of the Housing Land Supply Act 2018 .

6. Repeal of Act
    This Act is repealed on the first anniversary of the day on which this Act received the Royal Assent.
